claim: Up All Night was released by a record label.
premise_source_doc_sentence: RSO managed the careers of several superstars  (  Bee Gees , Yvonne Elliman , Eric Clapton , Andy Gibb  )  , and , as a record label , released the soundtracks to Fame , Sparkle , The Empire Strikes Back , Return of the Jedi , Times Square , Grease  (  over 30 million copies sold worldwide  )  , and Saturday Night Fever  (  over 35 million copies sold worldwide  )  .
